episodes.title: Cult Mom Lori Vallow Daybell: Her New Jailhouse Interview’s Most Shocking Revelations
episodes.description:
In a jailhouse interview with Dateline’s Keith Morrison, Lori Vallow Daybell, convicted of murdering her two children, Tylee Ryan and Joshua “JJ” Vallow, maintains her innocence and asserts that she and her husband, Chad Daybell, will be exonerated, claiming divine visions of their release. During the combative exchange, Vallow Daybell attempts to shift blame for JJ’s death onto her deceased daughter, Tylee, a narrative refuted by authorities due to the confirmed timeline of their deaths.￼ This interview offers a rare glimpse into Vallow Daybell’s psyche as she continues to proclaim her innocence despite overwhelming evidence and a life sentence.
